Form990ScheduleIPartIV.Identifier: Procedure for Monitoring Grants in the U.S.:
Form990ScheduleIPartIV.Explanation: Schedule I, Part I, Line 2: Organizations submit applications for grants. These applications are presented to committees of the Foundation, who determine if the request meets the requirements of the grant funds available. If the request meets the requirements, the committee may approve the request and an amount to be granted to the organization.
